fields.name: White and Gold Stud Earrings
fields.description: Beautifully simple and light weight studs. Wear during the day to add some glamour or add to your evening outfit for a splash of understated elegance. For pierced ears only.

fields.name: Colourful Clay Earring
fields.description: These earrings are bright and colourful, adding a touch of fun to any outfit. Made from polymer clay, they are lightweight but durable. Perfect for someone who loves splashes of colour!

fields.name: White Hoop Speckled Clay Earrings
fields.description: These white speckled circular drop earrings are the perfect statement earrings to add to any outfit. Made from P:olymer Clay, they are lightweight and durable whilst still being stylish.

fields.name: Polkadot Tassel Earring
fields.description: Stud, Tassel Drop earrings with a black and white zebra print with colourful polkadots. Light weight and very unique, these will uplift any outfit.

fields.name: White Clay Drop Earring
fields.description: Simple and yet full of colour, these earrings will add a splash of something bright to your day.

fields.name: Gold Pearl Earring
fields.description: Not our usual Polymer Clay, these gold pearl earrings are elegant and glamourous.

fields.name: Blue Bead Tassel Earring
fields.description: These turquoise blue tassel earring come with a single simple but stunning turquoise bead and gold earring hooks. Although simple, it's the small details that make this earring very special.

fields.name: Blue Drop Earrings
fields.description: Blue drop earrings with silver stud piercing. Light weight and simple with a bold blue translucent drop to add style and various depths of colours dependant on the light.

fields.name: Gold Face Earrings
fields.description: In-trend gold face drop earrings will add a bohemian flare to your outfit. Not our usual clay creations but still just as beautiful, as with all of our earrings these are lightweight and durable, perfect to see you from day into night.

fields.name: Black and White Statement Studs
fields.description: These black and white stud drop earrings are bold without being too bright. Perfect for those who prefer a monochrome palate.

fields.name: Sloth Necklace
fields.description: This cute sloth necklace is perfect for those who are quirky and love to add something different to their outfit. Made from Polymer Clay, this necklace is durable and easy to clean.

fields.name: Rose Gold Chain
fields.description: This simple rose gold chain is perfect as a layering piece or on its own paired with one of our colourful clay earrings.
